      "bestial": "<strong>Deviation -- Bestial:</strong> When {{DISPLAY:vars.alterEgoName}} takes control, {{NAME}} loses touch with {{his}} humanity. Sapient thought eludes {{him}}, and {{his}} higher brain functions erode. At best, this causes stronger fight-or-flight instincts; at worst, it turns {{NAME}} into a mindless beast. {{DISPLAY:vars.alterEgoName}} suffers the {{TOOLTIP:Bestial Condition,json.conditions.bestial}}, which does not resolve until the end of the scene. {{He}} can't build equipment or plan ahead for a scene beyond the current one."
